We actually drove there from the UK, and the valet met us, and deposited our car in the garage - the parking was included in the price, so that was nice.	We took a Connexxion hotel shuttle from the Schiphol airport, and the trip took about 25-30 minutes (with a few other hotel drop-offs).	Parking was 50 Euros a night, but that was to be expected here.	Everything worked properly and was explained by the valet.	The concierge staff were also very efficient and helpful in terms of providing dinner reservations and transport services.